OL,3,C'This is all in Grace's name', says
OL,4,Cfather as Nottingham attack inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FThe father of Nottingham attack victim
OL,8,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar has told ITV News
OL,9,FLondon that his family's fight for
OL,10,Fanswers into the events leading up to
OL,11,Fher death will be his daughter's
OL,12,Flegacy.
OL,14,FUniversity student Grace, from
OL,15,FWoodford Green, was killed alongside
OL,16,Fher friend Barnaby Webber and
OL,17,Fcaretaker Ian Coates by the paranoid
OL,18,Fschizophrenic Valdo Calocane in
OL,19,FNottingham in June 2023.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
