CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1772136279
OL,3,C'This is all in Grace's name', says
OL,4,Cfather as Nottingham attack inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FA public inquiry began on Monday, with
OL,8,Fthe families of the victims saying the
OL,9,Fprobe is about "holding those who
OL,10,Fneglected their jobs to account".
OL,12,FSpeaking before the start of the
OL,13,Finquiry, Grace's father Dr Sanjoy
OL,14,FKumar told ITV News London: "We know
OL,15,Fwhat happened. It's a question of why
OL,16,Fdid it happen?
OL,18,F"Today's the start of all the answers
OL,19,Fthat we're going to get for the
OL,20,Fquestions that remained unanswered.
OL,26,@qD@POUrD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1772136279
OL,3,C'This is all in Grace's name', says
OL,4,Cfather as Nottingham attack inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,F"There are so many things that could
OL,8,Fhave been done to prevent, but they
OL,9,Fweren't.
OL,11,F"Today, I hope we are going to get a
OL,12,Fcount from people who didn't do their
OL,13,Fjobs, and that is all I'm interested
OL,14,Fin."
OL,16,FProsecutors, police and medical
OL,17,Fprofessionals are due to be
OL,18,Fscrutinised by the two-year public
OL,19,Finquiry, which will be chaired by
OL,20,Fsenior retired judge Deborah Taylor.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1772136279
OL,3,C'This is all in Grace's name', says
OL,4,Cfather as Nottingham attack inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct (IOPC) previously prepared a
OL,9,Freport which concluded that officers
OL,10,Ffailed to properly investigate an
OL,11,Fassault on warehouse workers by
OL,12,FCalocane which could have stopped his
OL,13,Fkilling spree a month later.
OL,15,FDr Kumar said he hoped the findings of
OL,16,Fthe inquiry will prevent other
OL,17,Ffamilies from suffering the same loss
OL,18,Fas he has.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1772136279
OL,3,C'This is all in Grace's name', says
OL,4,Cfather as Nottingham attack inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,F"My wife and I and James, Grace's
OL,8,Fbrother, have lost the love of our
OL,9,Flives. But no other family should go
OL,10,Fthrough what we are going through."
OL,12,FHe added: "This is all in Grace's
OL,13,Fname. This is all in her legacy. She
OL,14,Fwas a beautiful person. She had so
OL,15,Fmuch to contribute.
OL,17,F"She was training to become a doctor
OL,18,Fherself. Such a loss to her, to her
OL,19,Ffriends, her family. We do everything
OL,20,Fin her name."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
