FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1772136279
OL,3,C'This is all in Grace's name', says
OL,4,Cfather as Nottingham attack inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FCalocane, who also attempted to kill
OL,8,Fthree more people during the attack,
OL,9,Fwas sentenced to an indefinite
OL,10,Fhospital order in January 2024 after
OL,11,Fadmitting manslaughter by diminished
OL,12,Fresponsibility and attempted murder.
OL,14,FThe sentence has been widely
OL,15,Fcriticised by the victims' families.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1772136279
OL,3,C'This is all in Grace's name', says
OL,4,Cfather as Nottingham attack inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FWhen the inquiry was announced, the
OL,8,FMinistry of Justice said the
OL,9,Fmanagement of Calocane's risk to
OL,10,Fothers in the lead-up to the attacks
OL,11,Fand public servants accessing
OL,12,Finformation without authorisation will
OL,13,Fform part of the inquiry.
OL,15,FDr Kumar said he hoped the inquiry
OL,16,Fwill mark a turning point in what has
OL,17,Fbeen a "bruising" two and a half years
OL,18,Ffor his family.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
