FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1772136279
OL,3,C'This is all in Grace's name', says
OL,4,Cfather as Nottingham attack inquiry
OL,5,Copens
OL,7,F"We feel we haven't had a chance to
OL,8,Fgrieve her because we've been involved
OL,9,Fin a fight right from the very
OL,10,Fbeginning when we heard so many things
OL,11,Fthat didn't make any sense.
OL,13,F"I hope after this we get a chance to
OL,14,Fgrieve."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/8
